            </a>
            <a href="#products"
              className="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-[#3FE56C] text-black text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold hover:bg-white hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(63,229,108,0.3)]">
              Secure Pre-Order
            </a>
